{"id": "1190720692925243512", "channel_id": "1190720692925243512", "type": 0, "author_id": "1190712196783677542", "author_name": "energetic_cheetah_58696", "author_bot": false, "content": "如圖所示 手上有兩張能抽1的牌\n牌堆沒有其他牌 抽了幾次卻抽不起來了\n請問這是遊戲機制還是bug\n如果看不懂 底下是影片\nhttps://youtu.be/Lr9n0SNtoQ8?feature=shared", "timestamp": "2023-12-30T18:18:55.714000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1190720693902512188", "filename": "Screenshot_20231231-020456.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1931175, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1190720692925243512/1190720693902512188/Screenshot_20231231-020456.png?ex=69ccb8cf&is=69cb674f&hm=36b896b00cb78ccf1b2e518c54c031ff9e1165a7f90dace0a094df5c448247f2&"}, {"id": "1190720694598762536", "filename": "Screenshot_20231231-020521.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2016834, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1190720692925243512/1190720694598762536/Screenshot_20231231-020521.png?ex=69ccb8d0&is=69cb6750&hm=3a1de07e57503404cfc27bfa9da7ab26140d78c752aedeb4265410419ab61649&"}, {"id": "1190720695026589846", "filename": "Screenshot_20231231-020543.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 646973, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1190720692925243512/1190720695026589846/Screenshot_20231231-020543.png?ex=69ccb8d0&is=69cb6750&hm=faf52775964a9e1f6e7346829b8c8bcafe729990073dd4d4348a9f2badb3b51d&"}, {"id": "1190720695479570563", "filename": "Screenshot_20231231-020559.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1028338, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1190720692925243512/1190720695479570563/Screenshot_20231231-020559.png?ex=69ccb8d0&is=69cb6750&hm=fa65fc6c5aaa3ec35b1de3d94ca63b87aeea4a40c8ee296cb13eaf40df70f26c&"}], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "忘卻前夜 3-13 這是遊戲正設還是bug?", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Lr9n0SNtoQ8", "description": "主要要用的牌2張\n簡單解釋一下手牌效果\n石質分解抽1 未被滿足之痛抽1\n牌堆裡沒其他牌\n正常來說是要\n滿痛再抽石質 石質再抽滿痛\n然後達成無限的\n結果抽個1.2次 牌就抽不上來了\n\n\n我後來去測試其他的牌也是一樣\n當回合同樣的牌只要丟到棄牌堆2次 就抽不起來了\n這是怎樣?\n是想限制玩家搞這種玩法才做這個設定嗎\n那乾脆連抽牌都拔掉好了\n\n本來以為可以靠這個想法等級1輕鬆過3-13來個完美收尾的\n害我對這個遊戲的分數從80分跌到剩下40 ㄏㄏ"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1190720692925243512", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」不能無限抽牌是遊戲機制還是bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
